prompt: What are the total sales by product category limit 2
sql_query: SELECT      c.CATEGORY_NAME,     SUM(CAST(DAILY_TOTAL_SALE AS DECIMAL(18,2))) as TOTAL_SALES FROM REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES c WHERE DAILY_TOTAL_SALE IS NOT NULL GROUP BY c.CATEGORY_NAME ORDER BY TOTAL_SALES DESC LIMIT 2;

prompt: What are the total sales by product category limit 2
sql_query: ```sql SELECT      V_SMM_DAILY_SALES.CATEGORY_NAME,     SUM(V_SMM_DAILY_SALES.DAILY_TOTAL_SALE) AS TOTAL_SALES FROM      REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES GROUP BY      V_SMM_DAILY_SALES.CATEGORY_NAME ORDER BY      TOTAL_SALES DESC LIMIT 2; ```

prompt: What are the total sales by product category top 4
sql_query: ```sql SELECT      V_SMM_DAILY_SALES.CATEGORY_NAME,     SUM(V_SMM_DAILY_SALES.DAILY_TOTAL_SALE) AS TOTAL_SALES FROM      REPORTING_UAT.GOLD_SALES.V_SMM_DAILY_SALES GROUP BY      V_SMM_DAILY_SALES.CATEGORY_NAME ORDER BY      TOTAL_SALES DESC LIMIT 4; ```
